obj_root_law_sections_1_content:
  string
  line `(1) This Act may be called the General Clauses Act, 1897; ^1`
  line ***
  line
  line ^2*****
obj_root_law_sections_1_footnotes:
  string
  line `1. The word "and" rep. by Act 10 of 1914, s. 3 and the Second Schedule.`
  line
  line `2. Sub-section (2) rep. by s. 3 and the Second Schedule, ibid.`
